                        SQUID Cache Manager 
			====================
                                    
http://docstore.mik.ua/squid/FAQ-8.html
http://wiki.squid-cache.org/SquidFaq/CacheManager

				    Setup 
				    =====

1. # mkdir /var/www/squid-cgi/

   This is under the home of user apache - /var/www/

2. # cp /usr/lib/squid/cachemgr.cgi  /var/www/squid-cgi/   

3. Configure httpd.conf :

   ScriptAlias /squid-cgi/ "/var/www/squid-cgi/"  [Line 578]

4. Restart Apache  # service httpd restart

5. Restart SQUID   # service squid restart

6. There are 2 ways to access the cache mgr info

     CLI :
        a. The squidclient CLI prg
	b. The cachemgr.cgi prg

        a. squidclient cache_object://cache.host.name/info
	   or simply 
        a. squidclient mgr:info

     Browser:
     
	b. The cachemgr.cgi prg
	
           lynx www.vashi.com/squid-cgi/cachemgr.cgi
           or 
           konqueror www.vashi.com/squid-cgi/cachemgr.cgi
   
        # squidclient mgr:info

